item.title: Fine-Grained Dynamic Framework for Bias-Variance Joint Optimization on Data Missing Not at Random
item.description: A new fine-grained dynamic framework jointly optimizes bias and variance for accurate predictions from missing-not-at-random data, surpassing existing methods.
